{"tid":1784731,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星Galaxy S11全新渲染圖出爐","createTime":"2019-12-16T01:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T06:20:16.000Z","uid":141060,"like":9,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"884bd7504f3a70d8e859e8a55b2f4d244a34c41b","tid":1784731,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T01:36:26.000Z","msg":"即將於2020年2月18日發布的三星Galaxy S11無疑是接下來最重磅的機型之一，其機身參數也大致曝光，現在唯一還有神秘感的的就是S11的機身設計。<br />\n<br />\n此前S11僅曝光過一張諜照，也只露出了機身背部，人們能看到的唯有一顆碩大無比的背部攝像頭區域，近日，有外媒LetsGoDigital根據這張諜照制作出了全新的渲染圖，讓我們一睹為快吧。<br />\n<br />\n核心規格方面，Galaxy S11采用6.7英寸AMOLED顯示屏，分辨率為QHD+，刷新率為120Hz，搭載高通驍龍865/Exynos 9830芯片，配備8GB LPDDR5內存+UFS 3.0閃存，後置一億像素，運行Android 10。<br />\n<br />\n此外，曝光的電池諜照顯示，Galaxy S11電池容量最小值為4370mAh，典型值為4500mAh，與Galaxy Note 10+一致，相比Galaxy S10 3400mAh有大幅提升。<br />\n<br />\n值得註意的是，Galaxy S11系列還有Galaxy S11e、Galaxy S11+等新品，傳聞Galaxy S11+僅提供5G版本，剩余兩款還有4Ｇ版本可供選擇。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.mydrivers.com/img/20191216/s_9bbde6a83268485db68c8c9b9c739640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.mydrivers.com%2Fimg%2F20191216%2Fs_9bbde6a83268485db68c8c9b9c739640.jpg&h=712b44d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.mydrivers.com/img/20191216/s_b9c33171552e4dd5944328185971c43e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.mydrivers.com%2Fimg%2F20191216%2Fs_b9c33171552e4dd5944328185971c43e.jpg&h=749df818&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img1.mydrivers.com/img/20191216/s_ba49e3b7ce3e4c4e85b4865586fea4d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.mydrivers.com%2Fimg%2F20191216%2Fs_ba49e3b7ce3e4c4e85b4865586fea4d4.jpg&h=c94c80c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.mydrivers.com/img/20191216/s_9a7722f5f1ce4166a68d7dbf7e541e35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.mydrivers.com%2Fimg%2F20191216%2Fs_9a7722f5f1ce4166a68d7dbf7e541e35.jpg&h=789ed52c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.mydrivers.com/img